<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Greener journeys, more thoughtful commutes">
    <title>CommuteGreen</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }

        /* Navigation bar styling */
        .navbar {
            background-color: #2a9d8f; /* Dark green */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .navbar-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo a {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .navbar-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .navbar-links li {
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        .navbar-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-links a:hover {
            color: #e9c46a; /* Light yellow */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-container">
                <div class="logo">
                    <a href="#home">CommuteGreen</a>
                </div>
                <ul class="navbar-links">
                    <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about">About me</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="home">
            <h2>Welcome to CommuteGreen</h2>
            <p>We're on a mission to give users a faster and greener commute.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <h2>About me</h2>
            <p>CommuteGreen is a project aiming to help users find better joruneys, while spreading awareness about the benefits of public transportation.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>E-mail: danielp@askeris.no</p>
        </section>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
